        <div class="sect-title-wrapper">
          <h2 class="sect-title">Stars Align</h2>
          <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>

      
  
      <div class="text-wrapper">    
        
        
          <p>Convinced there was a market for my whimsical low-tech creations, changing trends provided timely impetus (see below). So, in June 2022 I launched <span>HandDrawn</span><em>.Tech</em>, a place to license my inventive illustrations or to commission new ones. </p>
        

        
        

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         


         

         

